query.query: {"measures":[["avg","CallDurationInSeconds"],["sum","TotalCalls"]],"pigql":"a = load \"<ServiceActivity>\";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour', count() as 'sum_TotalCalls', avg('CallDurationInSeconds') as 'avg_CallDurationInSeconds';a = order a by 'time_Hour' asc;","autoFilter":true,"groups":[["time_Hour"]]}

{"measures":[["service","level"]],"pigql":"a = load \"<ServiceActivity>\";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = filter a by 'IsCall' == \"Yes\";a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',(1 - erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * exp(((((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds')) - unique('Owner.Id')) * 50 / avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Service_Level';a = group a by all; a = foreach a generate avg('Service_Level') as 'service_level'","autoFilter":true}

{"measures":[["prob","waiting"]],"pigql":"a = load \"<ServiceActivity>\";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = filter a by 'IsCall' == \"Yes\";a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) as 'er_c',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Probability_of_Waiting';a = group a by all; a = foreach a generate avg('Probability_of_Waiting') as 'prob_waiting'","autoFilter":true}

{"measures":[["Probability","of_Waiting",null,{"display":"Waiting"}],["Service","Level"]],"pigql":"a = load \"<ServiceActivity>\";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = filter a by 'IsCall' == \"Yes\";a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) as 'er_c',erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Probability_of_Waiting',(1 - erlang_c(unique('Owner.Id'),(((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * exp(((((count() / unique('CreatedDate_Day'))/3600) * avg('CallDurationInSeconds')) - unique('Owner.Id')) * 50 / avg('CallDurationInSeconds'))) * 100 as 'Service_Level';a = order a by 'time_Hour' asc;","autoFilter":true,"groups":[["time_Hour"]]}

{"measures":[["total","Agents"]],"pigql":"a = load \"<ServiceActivity>\";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day','CreatedDate_Hour');a = foreach a generate 'CreatedDate_Hour' as 'time_Hour',unique('Owner.Id') as 'total_Agents';a = order a by 'time_Hour' asc;","autoFilter":true,"groups":[["time_Hour"]]}

{"pigql":"a = load \"<ServiceActivity>\";a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}}; a = group a by 'Owner.Name';a = foreach a generate avg('CallDurationInSeconds') as 'avg_CallDurationInSeconds', unique('Case.Id') as 'sum_CaseId', 'Owner.Name' as 'Owner.Name', count() / unique('Case.Id') as 'avg_Calls_Per_Case';","measures":[["avg","CallDurationInSeconds",null,{"display":"Avg of Call Duration (Sec)"}],["avg","Calls_Per_Case",null,{"display":"Avg of Calls Per Case"}],["sum","CaseId",null,{"display":"Number of Cases"}]],"autoFilter":true,"groups":["Owner.Name"]}

{"pigql":"q = load \"<ServiceActivity>\";q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}}; q = group q by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');q = foreach q generate 'CreatedDate_Year'+\"~~~\"+'CreatedDate_Month'+\"~~~\"+'CreatedDate_Day' as 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day', unique('Id') as 'dailyCalls',avg(unique('Id')) over ([..] partition by all ) as 'avg_dailyCalls',sum(1) over ([..] partition by all) as 'Counter';q = group q by 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day';q = foreach q generate 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day' as 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day', power(first('dailyCalls') - (first('avg_dailyCalls')),2)/first('Counter') as 'sqr_diff_dailyCalls',first('avg_dailyCalls') as 'avg_dailyCalls',first('dailyCalls') as 'dailyCalls';q = group q by 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day';q = foreach q generate 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day' as 'CreatedDate_Year~~~CreatedDate_Month~~~CreatedDate_Day', first('dailyCalls') as 'total_dailyCalls', first('avg_dailyCalls') as 'avg_dailyCalls',first('avg_dailyCalls') + (3 * sqrt(sum(sum('sqr_diff_dailyCalls')) over ([..] partition by all))) as 'l_UCL',first('avg_dailyCalls') - (3 * sqrt(sum(sum('sqr_diff_dailyCalls')) over ([..] partition by all))) as 'l_LCL';","measures":[["total","dailyCalls",null,{"display":"Daily Calls"}]],"autoFilter":true,"groups":[["CreatedDate_Year","CreatedDate_Month","CreatedDate_Day"]]}

query.query: {"measures":[["avg","Call_Per_Agent"]],"pigql":"a = load \"<ServiceActivity>\"; a = filter a by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, \"Current\").asDateRange(\"date('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day')\")}};a = group a by ('CreatedDate_Year','CreatedDate_Month','CreatedDate_Day');a = foreach a generate count() / unique('Owner.Name') as 'avg_Call_Per_Agent';a = group a by all;a = foreach a generate avg('avg_Call_Per_Agent')  as 'avg_Call_Per_Agent';","autoFilter":true}

lens_2.query: q = load "<ServiceActivity>"; q = filter q by {{cell(Time_Selection.selection, 0, "Current").asDateRange("date('Case.CreatedDate_Year', 'Case.CreatedDate_Month', 'Case.CreatedDate_Day')")}}; q = filter q by 'IsCall' == "Yes"; q = foreach q generate 'Case.CaseNumber', first('Case.Account.Name') as 'Account Name', first('Owner.Name') as 'Owner.Name', first('CallDisposition') as 'CallDisposition', first('CallType') as 'CallType', first('Case.Reason') as 'Case.Reason',first('Status') as 'Status',first('Case.Product_Family_KB__c') as 'Product Family', avg('CallDurationInSeconds') as 'avg_CallDurationInSeconds'; q = limit q 100;
